    <item>
      <title>液化天然气贸易商选择付款而非运往德国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/lng-traders-choose-to-pay-rather-than-shipping-to-germany</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据中国国有终端运营商称，一些液化天然气贸易商选择对最初打算运往德国的供应支付费用，以便在亚洲获取更高的利润。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/lng-traders-choose-to-pay-rather-than-shipping-to-germany</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Oct 2024 16:06:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
